FlowViz

This tool is for simulating and visualizing flow from
Digital Elevation Models

Requirements
------------
1. GLUT/xf86vmode
2. GDAL

To build
--------
$ make

To run
------
$ ./flowviz <DEM> <latitude> <longitude> 

for <DEM>: you need to download the Philippines-SRTM4.1.zip file
-extract the necessary files

sample run
-------
./flowviz data/srtm_61_09.asc 14.13054 121.19048


Sample Coordinates
------------------
Mt. Makiling (14.13054, 121.19048)
Mt. Mayon (13.2552, 123.686)
Taal (14.002, 120.993)
Mt. Banahaw (14.06394, 121.42523)
Mt. Isarog (13.6667 123.383)
